{"tid":1385583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術][重要]要贏嘅黃金法則—出奇不意","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:14:00.000Z","uid":265195,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ed4173f63c3342ae13dedd82eb7006a75d5cb6fc","tid":1385583,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:11:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結論：<span style=\"color: red;\">不要說「pish」<br />\n試著說「留tg」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家連登最大嘅問題係未maximize行動力。連登有創意，有人數，有號召力，依幾日，好多人提出咗唔少從未用過嘅好橋，包括：<span style=\"color: red;\">屎蜢放狗宿、用laser射狗、接仔放工、助養計劃</span>，甚至好耐之前黃背心接管隧道收費站，依啲都係未出現過，而又極好嘅idea，咁點解冇人做？<span style=\"color: red;\">咪因為你哋花太多時間去討論細節囉！</span>唔好以為度好橋，萬無一失就最好，啲popo mon緊post架，等你地喺連登討論完，佢都部署好晒啦！以後，一見到<span style=\"color: red;\">多正評</span>嘅idea，善用連登app去篩檢最多正評嘅comment(<span style=\"color: red;\">閃電制</span>，見底欄)，覺得冇問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">請即做</span>。開tg組人傾戰術，殺佢一個措手不及。當依種風氣變左習慣，popo就會草木皆兵，唔崩潰都難！<br />\n<br />\n跟我講一次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要說「pish」<br />\n試著說「留tg」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：學術討論</span>"},{"pid":"4f4e5a1bc1a2d4007ef42e2e7125ac3dbddeba28","tid":1385583,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68ee4db433750dae0dd0ae8a0856c9185832ca6","tid":1385583,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d38179a8ca022854478c55bdba8d72cf55210f7","tid":1385583,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:13:22.000Z","msg":"夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自